Noto Sans fonts bundled for PDF in-place text re-insertion.

Source: Google Noto Fonts (https://fonts.google.com/noto)
License: SIL Open Font License 1.1 (OFL)
See: https://openfontlicense.org/

Files:
- NotoSans-Regular.ttf
- NotoSans-Bold.ttf
- NotoSans-Italic.ttf
- NotoSans-BoldItalic.ttf
- NotoSansJP-Regular.ttf  (CJK fallback — Japanese/Chinese/Korean glyphs)

Note: PyMuPDF (pymupdf) is AGPL-3.0 licensed.
This font bundle has no additional license restrictions.
